rows.label: tlk42100151_03_msg0001
rows.name:
I met a Phonex from another country
the other day.

rows.label: tlk42100151_03_msg0002
rows.name:
They said they secretly boarded a Divine Beast ship
that arrived at Port Ananyam.

rows.label: tlk42100151_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I was surprised to see them.
Their build was about the same as mine.

rows.label: tlk42100151_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I was absolutely sure that being raised in Superbia
would make us thinner, but surprisingly,
we're the same.

rows.label: tlk42100151_03_msg0005
rows.name:
We're made to grow well even in cold or hot
places, or places with little water or plants.
